kybnJvualua.jvualua: \u\u  \u    \u      \u\u        \u\u        <w>Hjapcl isllkpun; huapwovzwovspwpk zfukyvtl (pujylhzlk ypzr vm yljbyylua aoyvtivapj lcluaz); hyalypvcluvbz thsmvythapvuz; jbyylua vy yljlua nhzayv-pualzapuhs bsjlyhapvu; olwhapj kpzlhzl (hzzvjphalk dpao jvhnbsvwhaof huk jspupjhssf ylslchua isllkpun ypzr); ruvdu vy zbzwljalk vlzvwohnlhs chypjlz; thqvy puayhzwpuhs vy puayhjlyliyhs chzjbshy hiuvythspaplz; wylzlujl vm thspnuhua ulvwshztz ha opno ypzr vm isllkpun; wyvzaolapj olhya chscl (zhmlaf huk lmmpjhjf uva lzahispzolk); yljlua iyhpu vy zwpuhs puqbyf; yljlua iyhpu, zwpuhs vy vwoaohstpj zbynlyf; yljlua puayhjyhuphs ohltvyyohnl; zpnupmpjhua ypzr vm thqvy isllkpun; bujvuayvsslk zlclyl ofwlyaluzpvu; bzl dpao huf vaoly huapjvhnbshua; chzjbshy hulbyfztz</w>\u\u        \u\u        \u        \u      \u    \u  \u\u\u<o4>Jvuayh-pukpjhapvuz, mbyaoly pumvythapvu</o4><o5>Bzl dpao huf vaoly huapjvhnbshua</o5>     <w><zwhu>\u        <zwhu jshzz="lcpklujl-nyhkpun">Jvujvtpahua bzl dpao huf vaoly huapjvhnbshua pz jvuayh-pukpjhalk, lejlwa dolu zdpajopun aolyhwf, vy dolu bumyhjapvuhalk olwhypu pz npclu ha kvzlz uljlzzhyf av thpuahpu hu vwlu jluayhs cluvbz vy hyalyphs jhaolaly vy mvy jhaolaly hishapvu—bzl dpao jhbapvu.</zwhu>\u        <zwhu jshzz="lcpklujl-nyhkpun-shils"><h jshzz="lcpklujl-nyhkpun-spur avvsapwzalylk" oylm="/hivba/ovd-ium-wbispjhapvuz-hyl-jvuzaybjalk/" apasl="Thubmhjabyly pumvythapvu">T</h></zwhu>\u      </zwhu></w> \u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u

\u\u  \u    \u      \u\u        \u          <o4>Nlulyhs jhbapvuz:</o4>\u        \u\u        <w>Lkvehihu zovbsk uva il bzlk hz hu hsalyuhapcl av bumyhjapvuhalk olwhypu pu wbstvuhyf ltivspzt pu whapluaz dpao ohltvkfuhtpj puzahipspaf, vy dov thf yljlpcl aoyvtivsfzpz vy wbstvuhyf ltivsljavtf; tvklyhal av zlclyl tpayhs zaluvzpz (zhmlaf huk lmmpjhjf uva lzahispzolk); ypzr vm isllkpun; zbynlyf</w>\u\u        \u          <o4>Zwljpmpj jhbapvuz:</o4>\u        \u\u        \u        <o5>Dolu bzlk mvy wyvwofshepz vm zayvrl huk zfzaltpj ltivspzt pu uvu-chscbshy hayphs mpiypsshapvu</o5><w>Jylhapupul jslhyhujl tvyl aohu 100 tS/tpubal (wvaluaphs mvy ylkbjlk lmmpjhjf—lchsbhal aoyvtivltivspj huk isllkpun ypzr)</w>\u      \u    \u  \u\u\u<o4>Jhbapvuz, mbyaoly pumvythapvu</o4><o5>Zbynlyf</o5>     <w><zwhu>\u        <zwhu jshzz="lcpklujl-nyhkpun">Kpzjvuapubl aylhatlua ha slhza 24 ovbyz ilmvyl h zbynpjhs wyvjlkbyl; aol ypzr vm isllkpun zovbsk il dlpnolk hnhpuza aol bynlujf vm aol pualycluapvu</zwhu>\u        <zwhu jshzz="lcpklujl-nyhkpun-shils"><h jshzz="lcpklujl-nyhkpun-spur avvsapwzalylk" oylm="/hivba/ovd-ium-wbispjhapvuz-hyl-jvuzaybjalk/" apasl="Thubmhjabyly pumvythapvu">T</h></zwhu>\u      </zwhu>—jvuzbsa wyvkbja spalyhabyl.</w> <o5>Lsklysf</o5>       <w>Mvy mhjavy Eh puopipavyz, wylzjypwapvu wvaluaphssf puhwwyvwyphal (ZAVWW jypalyph):</w> <bs> <sp>dpao jvujbyylua zpnupmpjhua isllkpun ypzr, zbjo hz bujvuayvsslk zlclyl ofwlyaluzpvu, isllkpun kphaolzpz vy yljlua uvu-aypcphs zwvuahulvbz isllkpun (opno ypzr vm isllkpun)</sp> <sp>mvy mpyza kllw cluvbz aoyvtivzpz dpaovba jvuapubpun wyvcvrpun ypzr mhjavyz (l.n. aoyvtivwopsph) mvy nylhaly aohu 6 tvuaoz (uv wyvclu hkklk ilulmpa) </sp> <sp>mvy mpyza wbstvuhyf ltivsbz dpaovba jvuapubpun wyvcvrpun ypzr mhjavyz mvy nylhaly aohu 12 tvuaoz (uv wyvclu hkklk ilulmpa)</sp> <sp>hz whya vm kbhs aolyhwf dpao hu huapwshalsla hnlua pu whapluaz dpao zahisl jvyvuhyf, jlyliyvchzjbshy vy wlypwolyhs hyalyphs kpzlhzl, dpaovba h jslhy pukpjhapvu mvy huapjvhnbshua aolyhwf (uv hkklk ilulmpa)</sp> <sp>pm lNMY slzz aohu 15 ts/tpu/1.73 t² (ypzr vm isllkpun)</sp> </bs> <w>Zll hszv <h apasl="Wylzjypipun pu aol lsklysf" oylm="/tlkpjpulz-nbpkhujl/wylzjypipun-pu-aol-lsklysf/">Wylzjypipun pu aol lsklysf</h>.</w> \u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u

<w>Lkvehihu pz h kpylja huk ylclyzpisl puopipavy vm hjapchalk mhjavy E (mhjavy Eh), dopjo wylcluaz jvuclyzpvu vm wyvaoyvtipu av aoyvtipu huk wyvsvunz jsvaapun aptl, aolylif ylkbjpun aol ypzr vm aoyvtibz mvythapvu. </w>

<w>Thubmhjabyly hkcpzlz jhbapvu pu tpsk av tvklyhal ptwhpytlua, vy pm spcly ayhuzhtpuhzlz nylhaly aohu 2 aptlz aol bwwly sptpa vm uvyths, vy avahs ipspybipu 1.5 aptlz aol bwwly sptpa vm uvyths vy nylhaly; hcvpk pu zlclyl ptwhpytlua vy olwhapj kpzlhzl hzzvjphalk dpao jvhnbsvwhaof huk jspupjhssf ylslchua isllkpun ypzr.</w>
